!begin_node lbox_set_bsldr

(!begin_liste) [Availability]

!item [Name:]
¯List Box Set Slider B® - Positioniert den Slider B einer Listbox.

!item [Opcode:]
175 (Subopcode 5)

!item [Syntax:]
void lbox_set_bsldr ( LIST_BOX *box, int16_t first, GRECT *rect );

!item [Description:]
Die Funktion positioniert den Slider-B einer Listbox. Es gilt:

!begin_xlist !short [Parameter]
!item [Parameter]
Meaning
!item [~]
~
!item [box]
Pointer to the list box structure
!item [first]
Index of the first visible entry
!item [rect]
Pointer to redraw rectangle or 0L
!end_xlist

(!B)Hint:(!b)
This function draws it within the redraw 
rectangle <(!I)rect(!i). The contents of the list box will not be updated, 
so one may have to call lbox_update.
If (!I)rect(!i) is 0L, then only the position of the slider objects will 
be altered, but the objects will not be drawn.

!item [(!nolink [Return]) Value:]
Die Funktion liefert kein Ergebnis zurck.

!item [Availability:]
The presence of this call should be checked for using
(!link [appl_getinfo][%apgi_7]) (Opcode 7).

!item [Group:]
Listboxen

!item [See Also:]
(!link [Binding] [Bindings for lbox_set_bsldr]) ~  lbox_free_items ~  lbox_cnt_items

(!ende_liste)



